@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Pending
Pending --> OnHold : review
OnHold --> Closed : submit
Closed --> Approved : reject
Approved --> Archived : cancel
Archived --> Shipped : update
Archived : entry / log hashtag
Shipped --> [*]
@enduml